{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Agentop\n### Local-First Multi-Agent Control Center\n*100% local LLM · Zero cloud dependency · Self-improving via DPO flywheel*",
      "x": -160,
      "y": -780,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "6"
    },

    {
      "id": "copilot",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## VS Code Copilot\n**Manager & Judge**\n- Delegates generation to local\n- Grades all outputs vs rubric\n- Only spends tokens on judgment\n- Retries with critique on failure\n- Logs DPO pairs on success",
      "x": -900,
      "y": -540,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "discord",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Discord\n**OpenClaw Interface**\n- Commands & task dispatch\n- Security alert channel\n- Escalation notifications\n- Job status updates",
      "x": 480,
      "y": -540,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "6"
    },

    {
      "id": "openclaw_llm",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## OpenClaw Local LLM\n**Autonomous Employee**\n- Locally trained on ops workflows\n- Receives tasks from Discord\n- Uses Agentop as its hands\n- Risk assessment before execution\n- LOW → run local\n- HIGH → escalate to Claude\n- FAIL → escalate + log DPO pair",
      "x": 380,
      "y": -280,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 240,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "prompt_engineer",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Prompt Engineer\n**Pre-Routing Stage** *(missing — next build)*\n- KB context injection\n- Token optimization (merged)\n- Structured intent extraction\n- Feeds enriched payload to router",
      "x": -900,
      "y": -280,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "3"
    },

    {
      "id": "lex_router",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## lex-v3 Router\n**3-Tier Routing**\n① C fast (~0.01ms) — unambiguous keywords\n② LLM Ollama (~800ms) — intent classification\n③ Python keyword — fallback\n\n*Every decision logged → training data*",
      "x": -380,
      "y": -280,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "firewall",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## OpenClaw Firewall\n- 12 red-line patterns\n- Rate limit: 30 req/min\n- Blocked exfil domains\n- User ban list",
      "x": 740,
      "y": -280,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "1"
    },

    {
      "id": "orchestrator",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## LangGraph Orchestrator\n**Agentop Core**\n- Stateful agent routing\n- Fan-out via DeerFlow TaskDelegator\n- DriftGuard invariant enforcement\n- All inter-agent comms route through here\n- Never direct agent-to-agent calls",
      "x": -380,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "deerflow",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## DeerFlow Fabric\n**Intelligence Nervous System**\n- ExecutionRecorder → JSONL trajectories\n- ExecutionAnalyzer → post-run LLM critique\n- ToolHealthMonitor → failure rate tracking\n- ToolRepairEngine → proactive fix suggestions\n- FactMemory → per-agent long-term memory\n- ProgressiveSkillLoader → token-efficient skills\n- MiddlewareChain → before/after hooks",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 240,
      "color": "5"
    },

    {
      "id": "mcp_server",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## MCP Server ✅ NEW\n`GET /mcp/sse`\n`POST /mcp/messages`\n\nTools exposed to Copilot:\n- agentop_chat\n- agentop_webgen\n- agentop_content_draft\n- agentop_security_scan\n- agentop_research",
      "x": -900,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "5"
    },

    {
      "id": "agents_core",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Core Agents (11)\nsoul_core · devops · monitor\nself_healer · code_review\nsecurity · data · comms\ncs · it · knowledge",
      "x": -580,
      "y": 280,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "tools_layer",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Tool Layer\n13 native tools\n26 MCP tools (Docker bridge)\n8 browser tools (Playwright)\nGLM-OCR sidecar (port 5002)",
      "x": -280,
      "y": 280,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 100,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "ollama",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Ollama\n*Local LLM Engine*\nllama3.2 · lex-v3 (router)\nGemma 3 12B (via OpenRouter)\nAll inference stays on-device",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 280,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 110,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_store",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Memory Store\nNamespaced JSON per agent\nFact Memory (DeerFlow)\nVector KB (cosine search)\nRun trajectories (JSONL)",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 280,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 110,
      "color": "4"
    },

    {
      "id": "webgen",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## WebGen Pipeline\nSitePlanner → PageGenerator\n→ SEO → AEO → QA → Export\n\nUX scorer + retry loop\nSandbox gate before release\nDPO pairs from regen loops\nGallery tracking per build",
      "x": -1100,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 170,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "content_farm",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Content Farm\nTrendResearcher → [greenlight]\n→ ScriptWriter → Voice*\n→ Avatar/Higgsfield* → Caption\n→ QA → Publisher\n\nPRE-GEN: prompt quality scorer\nPOST-GEN: GLM-OCR thumbnail read\nRETRY: critique-regen loop\nLEARN: failure → DPO pair\n*stub — needs wiring",
      "x": -780,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 210,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "security_plane",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Security Plane\n*Proactive Mode (cron)*\n- Scan every 5min\n- alert_dispatch on anomaly\n- Event watcher → Discord alert\n\n*Reactive Mode*\n- Answers via OpenClaw/chat\n- Escalates high-risk to cloud\n\n*Future: Kali-trained model*",
      "x": -440,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 270,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "business_launcher",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Business Launcher\nDeerFlow orchestrates:\n① WebGen → site\n② Vercel publish button\n③ Content calendar start\n④ AI Receptionist deploy\n⑤ Analytics dashboard",
      "x": -100,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "ml_lab",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## ML Lab / Flywheel\nDecisionCollector → routing pairs\nWebGen regen → DPO pairs\nContent retries → DPO pairs\nReceptionist convos → SFT data\nCopilot retries → DPO pairs\n\nTraining pipeline → lex-v3\nEval gate → golden set\nModel swap → zero downtime",
      "x": 200,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 270,
      "height": 190,
      "color": "6"
    },

    {
      "id": "vercel_publish",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Vercel\n*Publish Button — NOT pipeline*\nUser names project\n→ vercel deploy --prod\n→ Link returned\nManual gate, on demand",
      "x": -1100,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "social_output",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Social Platforms\nTikTok (OAuth ✅)\nMeta (creds missing)\nYouTube (stub)\nScheduled publishing",
      "x": -820,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 110,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "ai_receptionist",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## AI Receptionist\n*Separate Service*\nTwilio + DO droplet\nCalls Agentop /chat\nfor reasoning & KB lookup\nAgentop = brain\nReceptionist = voice",
      "x": -560,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "discord_alerts",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Discord Alerts\nSecurity anomalies\nSystem health events\nEscalation notices\nJob completions",
      "x": -280,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 110,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "training_data",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Training Data\ndata/dpo/*.jsonl\ndata/training/*.jsonl\n→ lex-v3 fine-tuning\n→ Higgsfield prompt model\n→ OpenClaw ops model\nSelf-improving over time",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "6"
    },

    {
      "id": "skills_system",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Skill System\n22 manifest skills\n17 legacy domain packs\nProgressiveLoader → inject only relevant\nToggle via /skills API",
      "x": 680,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "4"
    }
  ],

